name: Frida Punk 014 - The Show must go on
description: Fun fact: Leading up to 1953 Fridas health had deteriorated significantly and she was having to move round on crutches or a wheelchair. Undeterred, as her first Solo exhibition was due to take place, Frida didn't want to miss out so she had an ambulance take her to the opening and was wheeled around at the event in style on a stretcher.
